ygData.subject: RE: [eqbards] Song Damage
ygData.msgSnippet: I ve found FCC to be pretty reliable against yellow and below mobs.  The double resist rate problems you have with Lullaby don t appear to work the same way
ygData.messageBody:
I've found FCC to be pretty reliable against yellow and below mobs. The double
resist rate problems you have with Lullaby don't appear to work the same way
with this song. In fact, I'm inclined to believe the mob only gets one chance
to resist. And if it sticks, then it helps getting your other songs to stick.
I've had this song memmed every since I got it.

Galtin
